# LLM Prompt Purify API Tests
# Use with VS Code REST Client or IntelliJ HTTP Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5147
@apiVersion = v1

### Health Check
# Test that the API is running and responsive
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

### Swagger Documentation
# Access the OpenAPI documentation
GET {{baseUrl}}/swagger/v1/swagger.json
Accept: application/json
